<h4 id="the-most-important-and-most-common-mistake-people-make-with-position-sticky-is-that-it-depends-on-top-to-work-i-have-my-top-set-to-55-in-the-sidebar-wrap-div-and-sticky-on-my-sidebar-div-its-important-so-dont-forget--see-what-i-did-there">The most important and most common mistake people make with position: sticky is that it depends on top to work. I have my top set to 5.5 in the sidebar-wrap div and sticky on my sidebar div. it’s !important so don’t forget! ;) see what I did there?</h4>

<h3 id="things-this-project-taught-me">Things this project taught me</h3>

